```plantuml
@startuml yoshixmk_remarks

actor User as U
participant "Chrome Extension" as CE
participant "Deno Web Server" as DWS
participant "FaunaDB" as FDB
participant "GitPress Blog" as GPB

U -> CE: Record Remark
CE -> DWS: Send Remark Data
DWS -> FDB: Store Remark (GraphQL Mutation)
FDB --> DWS: Acknowledge Storage

U -> DWS: View Remarks
DWS -> FDB: Fetch Remarks (GraphQL Query)
FDB --> DWS: Return Remarks Data
DWS -> U: Display Remarks

U -> DWS: View Travelogue
DWS -> GPB: Fetch RSS Feed
GPB --> DWS: Return Travelogue Content
DWS -> U: Display Travelogue

@enduml
```